measurements.description:
Eighteen flowers and three buds on 21 33-cm inflorescences;
	on a well-grown, clean plant of 34cm x 27cm in a 15-cm clay pot;

	dorsal sepal burnt orange heavily overlaid dark red, cauda oxblood;
	lateral sepals blood red obscurely striated black-red, caudae oxblood;
	petals white;
	lip saturated oxblood;  
	substance heavy; texture matte. Reference additional award #20185576.
